msgstr "Relação com Dev Services existentes"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/compose-dev-services.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Compose Dev Services work alongside existing Dev Services implementations provided by Quarkus extensions.\n"
